snippet.title: Gravity Shots for iOS and Android
snippet.description:
Protect the star from incoming orbs by shooting them out of the sky. Hit as many orbs as you can with each shot by bouncing the shots between orbs and predicting how gravity will affect the shot's trajectory.

Get it on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.funonium.gravityshots

Get it on Apple devices:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/gravity-shots/id1330331503?ls=1&mt=8
